| [[maxwell (unit)|maxwell]] (CGS unit)
| Mx
| ≡ 10&lt;sup&gt;−8&lt;/sup&gt; Wb&lt;ref name=nistguide&gt;{{citation | title=NIST Guide to SI Units, Appendix B.9 | url=http://physics.nist.gov/Pubs/SP811/appenB9.html | accessdate=August 27, 2009}}&lt;/ref&gt;
