| = 3.7{{e|10}} Bq &lt;ref name=&quot;SP811-2008&quot;&gt;Ambler Thompson &amp; Barry N. Taylor. (2008). [http://physics.nist.gov/cuu/pdf/sp811.pdf ''Guide for the Use of the International System of Units (SI)''.] Special Publication 811. Gaithersburg, MD: [[National Institute of Standards and Technology]]. p. 10.&lt;/ref&gt;
