    2) Please consider placing detailed or controversial material in the daughter article [[Demographics of California]].

Please try to keep this section of this central article to well-sourced, overview information. The daughter article is available for detailed information or information that may be disputed or controversial. --&gt;

===Population===

[[Image:California population map.png|thumb|300px|right|The population density of California.]]

{{US Census population
| 1850 = 92597
| 1860 = 379994
| 1870 = 560247
| 1880 = 864694
| 1890 = 1213398
| 1900 = 1485053
| 1910 = 2377549
| 1920 = 3426861
| 1930 = 5677251
